## Do not

- Require public Drive sharing — use OAuth (`newsletter:google-login`) or manual download + `--skip-download`
- Require Vercel, AI Gateway, or `OPENAI_API_KEY` for the standard workflow
- Commit `*.raw.json` files (gitignored)
- Skip the refine step — raw parsed JSON is not publish-ready
